  "description": {
   "en": "A tale of a husband who works non-stop at an exploitative company, and his adorable, white-haired wife who heals his daily fatigue when he comes home from work.  \n  \n\n\n---\n\n  \n**Links:**  \n- [![](https://i.imgur.com/dQCXZkU.png) Mangaka's Twitter](https://twitter.com/gggrande)  \n- [![](https://i.imgur.com/oiVINmy.png) Mangaka’s Pixiv](https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/1859092)  \n- [Mangaka’s YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChBJJdB_xGIqHqvv5tid18w)",
